<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= @model.name %> - –ü—Ä–æ—Å–º–æ—Ç—Ä 3D –º–æ–¥–µ–ª–∏</title>

  <script src="https://cdn.babylonjs.com/babylon.js"></script>
  <script src="https://cdn.babylonjs.com/loaders/babylonjs.loaders.min.js"></script>
  <script type="module" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@babylonjs/viewer@7.52.1/dist/babylon-viewer.esm.min.js"></script>

  <style>
    .model-container {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 20px auto;
    }

    .model-header {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .model-description {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #333;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .download-link {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #007bff;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 15px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    .download-link:hover {
      background: #0056b3;
    }

    .viewer-container {
      width: 100%;
      height: 500px;
      margin-top: 15px;
    }

    babylon-viewer {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="model-container">
    <div class="model-header"><%= @model.name %></div>
    <p class="model-description"><%= @model.description %></p>
    <a class="download-link" href="<%= rails_blob_path(@model.file, disposition: 'attachment') %>">
      üì• –°–∫–∞—á–∞—Ç—å –º–æ–¥–µ–ª—å
    </a>

    <div class="viewer-container">
      <babylon-viewer 
        source="<%= rails_blob_url(@model.file) %>" 
        skybox="https://assets.babylonjs.com/environments/environmentSpecular.env">
      </babylon-viewer>
    </div>    
  </div>
</body>
</html>
